Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,P-01s?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Co tu děláš?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:48.21,spell,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur1.2\fs45\fax-0.1\bord9.75\c&H181818&\pos(717,310.5)\frz11.113\3c&H1B241A&}List of \NInstructor's \NComments
