Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tady jsem tě nečekala.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Zametáš?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:52.17,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur20\c&H1E1E1E&\fad(400,600)\an7\pos(162,814)}11:01 A.M. \N Cemetery in Okutama
