Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The theme of today's joint Student Council and Chancellor meeting is:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's help Aoi's big confession go well."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.66,spell,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur1\fs105\bord3\c&H3439FE&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1368,336)\frz353.441}Sponsor: {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H1E2FF5&}Neshinbara
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoi, you may proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenzo, how do you confess your feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you done it a bunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You just insulted me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, how about the letter tactic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Itemize everything you want to tell her beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:16:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, give her a letter rather than telling her outright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I just gotta write down why I fell for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly brother, it's quite easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply pour out your heart, citing all her good points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Her good points?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can put them into words...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't describe how her face is totally my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't describe
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,how I can see her panties through her apron when she squats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't describe the epicness of the curve going from her waist to her butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're spouting it out easily enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait! That list
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is missing something of dire importance for Tori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a boob man, yet you've failed to mention them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed that such a breast connoisseur as Tori hasn't mentioned them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He yaps about them every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he awkward around the girl he likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:59.79,hand,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs165\b0\blur1.5\fsp15\pos(345,729)\clip(39,471,90,774)\t(\clip(39,471,675,774))}BOOBS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can't say anything about your tits until I grope them."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Poetic enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly brother, you don't take boobies lightly, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Believe it or not, I take 'em seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't trust your eyes, why don't you give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Try? Try what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You should ask someone with similar boobies to let you grope hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, you're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stupid even though you're smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is everyone lazing around out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nate! Prez!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! I heard the news, Tori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,About?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You asking a girl out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could drive you to commit such a dangerous act?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Horizon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Her, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:18:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but there's a chance she just resembles her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cool if she isn't Horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be damn incapable,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but I hope she'll stay by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you decide that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It got stuck in my head when I was thinking about how Horizon died
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,around this time ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided to confess how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to meet up with Masazumi and go visit Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Need me to relay a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna start the party here at eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so could you ask if he's coming or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge, judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I just remembered you have an important dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Use those.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitotsudaira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a perfect match for resolving a problem plaguing Tori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems rather important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the most important thing in my silly brother's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a serious matter pertaining to his proposal tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the chancellor's popping the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it might be beneath a member of the proud Mitotsudaira family,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,who branch off from the Matsudaira family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like I don't know the ways of ordinary people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never find a knight unwilling to help a commoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Nate Mitotsudaira, am happy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to lend you my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I shall present you my bosom to help you rehearse for the big event.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I won't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it, Sir Tori?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She was braless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe ya, Nate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare say otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, I hope she turns you down tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No holding back...
