Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.69,Default,,0,0,38,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:21.40,Default,,0,0,38,,No one's bringing goods in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean goods are being brought into Musashi but none are coming out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we're taking keepsakes of Mikawa before it dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now, watch your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That Jormungandr-level galley, Eikoumaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,belongs to Pope President Innocentius,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,who's affiliated with K.P.A. Italia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, the Pope President came to negotiate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the development of the Armaments of Deadly Sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Armaments of Deadly Sins...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They control part of the world's power balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of the eight armaments is capable of leveling entire cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The armaments' motifs are based
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,upon eight concepts taken from the Seven Deadly Sins.
