Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go back and play now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about investigating Remorse Way when I get back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursue the truth.
